<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0b1623" />
    <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.webmanifest" />
    <title>paste-lite</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        --bg: radial-gradient(circle at top right, #d9f0ff 0%, #f7fbff 45%, #ecf4ff 100%);
        --card: #ffffff;
        --text: #0f1f33;
        --sub: #53657d;
        --primary: #1776d2;
      }
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: "SF Pro Text", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      }
      main {
        max-width: 760px;
        margin: 48px auto;
        padding: 24px;
      }
      .card {
        background: var(--card);
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(17, 44, 73, 0.08);
        padding: 24px;
      }
      h1 {
        margin-top: 0;
      }
      p {
        color: var(--sub);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      code {
        background: #edf4fc;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 2px 8px;
      }
      .tag {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-right: 8px;
        margin-top: 8px;
        background: #e9f3ff;
        color: var(--primary);
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 4px 10px;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="card">
        <h1>paste-lite</h1>
        <p>Cloudflare Pages + Workers 架构已完成初始化。</p>
        <p>前端界面将由 Gemini 实现，当前页面用于验证部署与 PWA 安装链路。</p>
        <p>健康检查：<code>GET /v1/health</code></p>
        <span class="tag">Pages</span>
        <span class="tag">Worker API</span>
        <span class="tag">PWA Ready</span>
      </section>
    </main>
    <script>
      if ("serviceWorker" in navigator) {
        navigator.serviceWorker.register("/sw.js").catch(() => {});
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>

